{
  "name": "Solar Beam",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/light/projectile-beam-yellow.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "solarBeam",
    "description": "<p>You store a radiant power within yourself for the duration. You gain 1 Charge plus another Charge each time you Sustain this Spell (up to a maximum of 4).</p><p><strong>Sunlight:</strong> Once on each of your turns while in an area of Sunlight, you can spend 1 AP to gain a Charge.</p><p><strong>Spell Attack:</strong> You can spend 1 AP to release all stored Charges and make an Area Spell Attack against the AD every target within a 4 Space Line. If you release 4 Charges, you make the Attack with ADV.</p><p><strong>Hit:</strong> The target takes 1 Radiant damage per Charge.</p><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> When you drop <strong>Solar Beam Charges</strong> effect Spell Attack will trigger. Remember to remove if you drop sustain.</em></p><p><em><strong>System Tip 2:</strong> Use on demand macro to add one additional charge for 1 AP.</em></p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Passive: Light Beacon</span></strong></span></p><p>For the duration of the Spell, the Light Level of any Space you occupy increases by 1.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Damage: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The damage increases by 1.</p><p><strong>Area: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The length of the Line increases by 6 Spaces.</p><p><strong>Burning Radiance: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> Each target makes a Repeated Physical Save. <strong>Save Failure:</strong> The target begins Burning for 1 minute. Burning damage from this Enhancementdeals Radiant damage.</p><p><strong>Blinding: (4 MP)</strong> Each target makes a Physical Save. <strong>Save Failure:</strong> The target is Blinded for 1 Round.</p>",
